Interface Sequence<T,C extends Sequence<T,C>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Collection<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.List<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Array, BaseArray, IntegerList, StringList, StringList, Versions

    public interface Sequence<T,C extends Sequence<T,C>>
extends java.util.List<T>
    A list with extended functionality, modeled on the Enumerable class in Ruby.
